32:53.493 --> 32:56.844
All of these school girls
were deaf, vulnerable.

32:56.844 --> 32:58.977
They couldn't even hear
the footsteps behind them.

33:01.283 --> 33:02.719
I'm a CPA.

33:02.719 --> 33:05.287
