could do something like that.

33:08.334 --> 33:10.466
Yeah, well, we do,
and DNA doesn't lie.

33:10.466 --> 33:11.467
Your brother did this.

33:11.467 --> 33:12.860
Dear God.

33:12.860 --> 33:14.035
