as an accessory.

33:16.559 --> 33:20.563
I don't know what's going on,
but I swear to you,

33:20.563 --> 33:22.217
I don't have a brother.

33:22.217 --> 33:25.177
Then who were you looking
for with that ancestry kit?

33:25.177 --> 33:27.875
My wife gave that
to me for my birthday.

33:27.875 --> 33:30.269
She told me they didn't
find any relatives.

33:34.099 --> 33:35.709
