33:42.455 --> 33:45.066
DNA doesn't lie.

33:45.066 --> 33:46.807
So the wife did.

33:50.289 --> 33:52.378
When are you
going to release my husband?

33:52.378 --> 33:53.727
He's completely innocent.

33:53.727 --> 33:57.513
He may be, but we need
to find his half-brother.

33:57.513 --> 33:59.994
- He doesn't have a brother.
- Mrs. Little, we know.

33:59.994 --> 34:01.865
