how did you get the results?

34:10.091 --> 34:12.441
Look, you have to talk to me.

34:12.441 --> 34:15.009
This is a murder investigation.

34:17.751 --> 34:20.188
Okay, okay.

34:27.543 --> 34:29.284
I was curious.

34:29.284 --> 34:31.591
I opened his email
before he did.

34:31.591 --> 34:32.766
Okay.

34:32.766 --> 34:34.985
And you read it,
and what did it say?

34:34.985 --> 34:38.076
On his family tree,
under parents,

34:38.076 --> 34:40.817
