to be a mistake.

34:43.516 --> 34:47.259
So I emailed the woman
listed as his mother.

34:47.259 --> 34:51.001
And she let you in
on her secret?

34:51.001 --> 34:53.917
Alan's birth mother
had an affair,

34:53.917 --> 34:57.225
