34:57.225 --> 35:01.142
And you decided not
to tell your husband?

35:01.142 --> 35:06.147
Alan thinks his adopted
parents are his real parents.

35:06.147 --> 35:07.453
Okay.

35:07.453 --> 35:09.629
I love my family,
I don't want them hurt.

35:09.629 --> 35:11.021
I understand.

35:11.021 --> 35:13.546
And we will do everything
we can to protect

35:13.546 --> 35:15.156
