35:15.156 --> 35:17.115
But we need
to catch this rapist

35:17.115 --> 35:19.291
before he hurts another girl.

35:27.603 --> 35:32.042
My husband forced me to give
up Alan to save our marriage.

35:34.044 --> 35:36.090
Did you have another son?

35:38.310 --> 35:40.529
Yeah, Ronnie.

35:40.529 --> 35:44.707
We've just had nothing
but conflict and issues.

35:44.707 --> 35:46.927
Can I ask about the issues?

35:50.931 --> 35:54.543
