between us both.

35:54.543 --> 36:01.159
I really tried my best, but we
just never really got along.

36:04.684 --> 36:06.425
Where is Ronnie now?

36:11.952 --> 36:13.910
- Ronnie Samuels.
- NYPD.

36:13.910 --> 36:15.608
I didn't do anything.

36:15.608 --> 36:17.000
- Whoa!
- Drop it!

36:17.000 --> 36:19.220
Drop the gun, Ronnie.

36:19.220 --> 36:20.395
Ronnie.

36:23.790 --> 36:26.358
Don't shoot?

36:26.358 --> 36:29.012
Now you're protecting me?
- Ronnie, Ronnie.

36:29.012 --> 36:30.318
You told them I was here?

36:30.318 --> 36:32.668
Ronnie, Ronnie.
Listen to me.

36:32.668 --> 36:35.236
I need you
to give me the gun, okay?

36:35.236 --> 36:37.586
Okay.
Drop the gun, there we go.

36:37.586 --> 36:38.587
There you go. Give me the gun.

36:38.587 --> 36:40.241
There we go.

37:02.176 --> 37:03.743
