37:03.743 --> 37:05.310
We can connect you
to Renee's murder

37:05.310 --> 37:06.702
and three of the rape vics.

37:06.702 --> 37:09.270
DNA, and all three
picked you out of a lineup.

37:09.270 --> 37:10.837
