37:49.223 --> 37:52.618
These girls--

37:52.618 --> 37:57.405
Logan Camacho,
Rose Salazar, Moreno West.

37:57.405 --> 37:58.972
They were victimized.

37:58.972 --> 38:02.367
We didn't listen,
