38:02.367 --> 38:04.456
But their rapes?

38:04.456 --> 38:06.545
That's on you.

38:06.545 --> 38:08.895
And Renee.

38:08.895 --> 38:10.592
She can't even speak
at all anymore.

38:10.592 --> 38:12.333
That wasn't
supposed to happen.

38:12.333 --> 38:13.813
She--she just hit her head.

38:13.813 --> 38:17.512
I wanna hear you say it!

38:17.512 --> 38:20.602
I raped them all.

38:23.170 --> 38:24.954
Are we satisfied now?

38:24.954 --> 38:26.434
No.

38:26.434 --> 38:29.132
Not until he writes it up
and signs it.

38:35.487 --> 38:37.184
I've been waiting
a long time for this.

38:41.623 --> 38:43.190
Can we get out
of the Bronx now?

38:43.190 --> 38:44.583
No chance, Fin.

38:44.583 --> 38:46.324
We have all those cases
